setTextFieldEnabled

public void setTextFieldEnabled(boolean state)
Enables or disables the text field. By default the text field is enabled. Disabling it causes only the button for date selection to be active, thus preventing the user from entering invalid dates. See http://dev.vaadin.com/ticket/6790.

Parameters:
state - true to enable text field, false to disable it.
